item.title: Mods help me run my server i give u 2mill rs gp if it works or u send me a one
item.dc:creator: @Tico135 Tico
item.description:
@Tico135 wrote:

Open your source. Find " runserver " on the list. Open it. This should work. If your server is hamachi, then open hamachi, and power it on. Create a network (Make a name and a password) and then click ok. Make sure you are entering the correct port also. Enter the ip ( if it is no-ip, enter the no-ip) otherwise, enter your ip-address that is on the top of the hamachi screen when you open it.
